<subSubSection id="E9E510E9FFD6BF02FF15C0ECFD0180E5" pageId="3" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="A1404362FFD6BF02FF15C0ECFD0180E5" blockId="3.[151,1437,151,1221]" pageId="3">
<emphasis id="938B9F70FFD6BF02FF15C0ECFEF280C0" bold="true" box="[199,326,943,968]" pageId="3">Etymology</emphasis>
. The epithet “santandereana” is a demonym alluding to the inhabitants of department of 
<collectingRegion id="633B8D80FFD6BF02FAFEC0ECFA2880C0" box="[1324,1436,943,968]" country="Colombia" name="Santander" pageId="3">Santander</collectingRegion>
